;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/ca525/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 75w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/650b0/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 150w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcSet=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/ca525/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 75w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/650b0/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 150w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 300w\" src=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png\" alt=\"Walk Ons Logo - Square\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/ca525/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 75w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/650b0/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 150w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/ca525/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 75w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/650b0/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 150w,\n/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png 300w\" src=\"/static/5405a1bcc927923dcb4b4c74b098f3aa/f2d49/Walk-Ons-Square-300x300.png\" alt=\"Walk Ons Logo - Square\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://walk-ons.com/\">Walk-Ons Bistreaux &amp; Bar</a>, recently voted as America’s Number One Sports Bar, made another game winning move by partnering with The PM Group! We’re proud to join their team to develop a successful branding strategy for their first San Antonio location and seven more to follow in other South Texas markets. The Louisiana style menu will feature Fried Alligator (tastes a lot like chicken), Duck and Andouille Gumbo and other Cajun seafood specialties as well as a wide variety of beverages to suit almost any taste.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nWalk-Ons is the dream come true of two former LSU basketball players Brandon Landry and Jack Warner, whose thorough dedication and hard work have grown their college project into the most popular sports bar concept in the country. Together we’ll make a winning team. Let’s play!!!  <br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\">About The PM Group</a>:</strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Scores New Client, Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Scores New Client, Walk-Ons Bistreaux &amp; Bar","url":"/pm-group-scores-new-client-walk-ons-bistreaux-bar/"}],"title":"The PM Group Scores New Client, Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar","metaDesc":"Walk-Ons Bistreaux & Bar was recently vot